  "description": {
    "zh": "有一个线人在车贩子那里开了个会，那是个秘密的地点。所以你他妈为什么还在这里待着？要是他已经被发现了，那你就去找一个藏身处，那里的钥匙也会在附近。找到所有他发现的情报。不要辜负我。",
    "en": "The informant set up a meeting near the car dealership, at a hidden spot? So why the hell are you still here? If he gets busted while you're still here, look for a hidden hideout, a spare key for it must be somewhere in there too. Find everything he's dug up. Don't let me down."
